    PrometheusServe -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR
    Training -->|creates| PyTorchJobCR["PyTorchJob CR"]

    %% External dependencies
    SDG -->|calls| TeacherModel["Teacher Model<br/>(KServe)"]
    MTBench -->|calls| JudgeModel["Judge Model<br/>(KServe)"]
    FinalEval -->|calls| JudgeModel
    Upload -->|pushes to| OCIRegistry["OCI Registry"]
    Upload -->|registers in| ModelRegistry["Model Registry"]

